Sentencas: A Ni-anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell ( SOFC) with a dense yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) thin film was fabricated.
Titulo: A direct ammonia tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The YSZ film was prepared using the vacuum I -assisted dip-coating method.
Titulo: A direct ammonia tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance of the single SOFC-based system running on ammonia was compared with that running on hydrogen.
Titulo: A direct ammonia tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C, the peak power densities were 202 and 200 with hydrogen and ammonia as the fuel, respectively.
Titulo: A direct ammonia tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A GC analysis of the effluent from the anode showed considerable amounts of nitrogen and hydrogen, but no trace of NO chi, when using ammonia as the fuel.
Titulo: A direct ammonia tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The ammonia performance is comparable to hydrogen, suggesting that ammonia can be an attractive alternative fuel.
Titulo: A direct ammonia tubular solid oxide fuel cell
